author: Renee Peters
title: Renee Peters
text: Love these guys! I'm one of those people who are really stupid when it comes to computers so luckily I got a step-by-step on how to install because my computer is also a piece of junk I bought a refurbished one that was supposed to come with windows 10 installed but turns out they only put the trial in and when I called for a product Q they never got back to me so I found this site through Google and I knew I would be chancing it because of the price but let's just be clear the price is just a perk! Really happy I even ended up getting Windows pro I couldn't ask for more.
